com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777292347602}]}\n323:[tool-call] delta {\"command\":\"find tests -path '*kotlin-stdlib-common*' -o -path '*kotlin*stdlib*common*' | head -50 && rg \\\"kotlin-stdlib-common\\\" -n .\",\"timeout\":10}\n324:[tool-call] end id=call_vYOgJ7jzz3MT7xZookmQqITA|fc_02c1dee4c1d605fa0169ef543e4fe48192a9326a3532879a68 name=bash args={\"command\": \"find tests -path '*kotlin-stdlib-common*' -o -path '*kotlin*stdlib*common*' | head -50 && rg \\\"kotlin-stdlib-common\\\" -n .\", \"timeout\": 10}\n325:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"**Searching for file related to coordinates**\\n\\nI need to find the right file that matches the coordinates I'm looking for. It's a simple task, but I want to ensure I’m thorough. I might get distracted, so I’ll focus on the specific location or data tied to the coordinates. It's important to keep my search organized, or I might end up lost in cluttered files! Okay, let's get started on this search and retrieve that file.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_02c1dee4c1d605fa0169ef543c76c48192a16137de9acc178c\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp71Q-IzkUXJFp0sIiqvYJxnWKpI6S_ZprV-O2N3PG_yChfQHxiD7cANRtcAHCmmI28tdtZTABbfq5ci38_C9pnJqjxZd09bhJ1kPB5wYZfVvBgtuafPeOQnpwMibu41pUbWRv9f1WOib40OB_vYPrRKmqRdZwkx4Rg-_iD9dMTNjJpayIgAxKvejsDehkJ36rMnV-IjjrW0dzxDHBWEtZL_10pqLv6ECMojnVNRD0XPZfQ8JgXtn2OXvPwHpFcscpR4y68wheUWmKT3XFUxW_VxGvlkEEK4Cqr5eglo2lyII00gO6-V0-zkmQ43E11sXRjOgQ_S7FJyxa9fdLZ5kGqmdmS-RcdPTSHfoGNMBFBfCO65noZMp6x3yH9_vyjAZLbSP28kfbegwEI0f6a5HCcqrFKSmcYLF___Cf7mBpVmi3K53nHJghDvsvhFHd5Zhc0jSjw9NYO3J3GHp6KWMTZS0-4F83zVez4acG0dWqinVz1ITiIGAVLDbCZfkpaUvR-3Wa0_weF4QQuHeuy2UFZKUxPQB2GvmumNlTvnEXELvrkmw9XSRr4wCdXlVftkMA7gu_ZXNtYDPUKya52inHNsDBWZYyU6ysOuA57oyRuop8HZzAehBsrJ4MWogvl0ltpIV8NT025Hv8C9R5ee5WZ1stWr